q 0.3 G 0.5 w 72 738 m 540 738 l S Q
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 72 710 Td (1. 5-4-3-2-1: Name 5 see, 4 touch, 3 hear, 2 smell, 1 taste) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 72 694 Td (2. Cold water on face/wrists - activates dive reflex) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 72 678 Td (3. Name items in the room by color) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 72 662 Td (4. Press feet firmly into floor - feel the ground) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 72 646 Td (5. Hold ice cubes until they melt) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 72 630 Td (6. Describe your surroundings out loud in detail) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 72 614 Td (7. Count backward from 100 by 7s) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 72 598 Td (8. Name state capitals or categories \(animals A-Z\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 72 582 Td (9. Touch different textures - describe each one) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 72 566 Td (10. Smell something strong \(peppermint, coffee, citrus\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 72 550 Td (11. Splash cold water on face) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 72 534 Td (12. Clench and release fists 5 times) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 72 518 Td (13. Orienting: look around room slowly, name what's here) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 72 502 Td (14. Butterfly hug \(cross arms, tap alternating shoulders\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 72 486 Td (15. Say your name, age, date, location out loud) Tj ET
